Instead of exporting env variables manually
aws configure set aws_access_key_id ASIA... --profile temp
aws configure set aws_secret_access_key wJalrXUtnFEMI/... --profile temp
aws configure set aws_session_token AQoDYXdzEJr... --profile temp


Perform execution using this profile:
aws s3 ls --profile temp





